728225f-a.title: Queens: Woodhaven Blvd - Penelope Street
728225f-a.text:
Woodhaven Boulevard, west side north of Penelope Street, showing
the Edxard Tompki s house of 1852. Nicholas Hasselberger owned it
in 1873. Other owners were J.J. Tompkins and J.T. Tompkins 1891 and
1896 respectively.
April 1923.
Euocene L. Armbruster Collection
